{
  "quicksight.dashboard.geospatialmapvisual.CfnAbout": "A geospatial map or a points on map visual.\n\nFor more information, see [Creating point maps](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/quicksight/latest/user/point-maps.html) in the *Amazon QuickSight User Guide*.",
